(553, 0, '_transient_dash_de3249c4736ad3bd2cd29147c4a0d43e', '<h4>Plus populaire</h4>\n<h5><a href=''http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/si-contact-form/''>Fast Secure Contact Form</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=si-contact-form&amp;_wpnonce=1c3350b941&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Fast Secure Contact Form''>Installer</a>)</span>\n<p>A super customizable contact form that lets your visitors send you email. Blocks all automated spammers. No templates to mess with.</p>\n<h4>Nouvelles extensions</h4>\n<h5><a href=''http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/linkmarklet/''>Linkmarklet</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=linkmarklet&amp;_wpnonce=d59882bae8&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Linkmarklet''>Installer</a>)</span>\n<p>Linkmarklet is an alternative to the Press This! bookmarklet aimed at rapid link blogging</p>\n<h4>Mises à jour récentes</h4>\n<h5><a href=''http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/front-file-manager/''>Front File Manager</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=front-file-manager&amp;_wpnonce=c54f47439e&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Front File Manager''>Installer</a>)</span>\n<p>Allow your visitors to upload files from front-end. You can list these files on any page using shortcode.</p>\n', 'no'),
